{"tid":1941567,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣立委陳柏惟拋邀香港人來台當兵","createTime":"2020-03-24T13:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T01:10:14.000Z","uid":198542,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"f98005e232455ebdc00e86390765e275bfc4483b","tid":1941567,"uid":198542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"香港反送中事件引發國內民眾關心支持，不少人更主張「今日香港、明日台灣」，提升台港互動親密度。台灣基進立委陳柏惟上午在立院質詢時建議，政府應邀香港人來台灣當兵。行政院長蘇貞昌則回應，「這個我看可能要更慎重」。<br />\n<br />\n陳柏惟表示，讓香港人來台灣當兵有三大好處，第一他們比我們年輕，<span style=\"color: red;\">第二他們更討厭中國</span>，第三可增加台灣勞工人數。蘇貞昌則說，「他們爭取自由民主我們是很關心」，但是否要讓香港人來台當兵，「這個我看可能要更慎重」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/4439024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F4439024&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=4567828a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/4439024</a>"},{"pid":"cbc2d69096554e12c39c103d206093287fee6250","tid":1941567,"uid":72749,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"hongkongers battalion<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7bb62cdc1036b1cb28b4e9879144c7df5706bc","tid":1941567,"uid":198542,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:15:40.000Z","msg":"香港人揸f16不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf47181952a73a97263c0e9fbfc4347123538e24","tid":1941567,"uid":34698,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:22:18.000Z","msg":"3Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a03f1959e55ce19699269b2bf61d2eeae43f668","tid":1941567,"uid":7736,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"聰明，出奇制勝，香港人對中共仇恨爆燈，<br />\n香港人對中共的仇恨，應該全世界國家上連同台灣人都比唔上，香港人打中